reviewText: I enjoyed this DVD, very erotic.  What can you expect it's Playboy.
The playmate were not sufficiently busty.

Playboy's Playmates Bustin' Out is fifty-five minutes long and was released on DVD on November 28, 2000. The whole video is a bunch of used clips from past Playboy videos. Eleven Playmates are featured in this video; meaning their segments was at least two minutes or more long.

Jenny McCarthy\Playboy Playmate of the Month for October 1993 & Playboy Playmate of the Year for 1994-Jenny has sex and undresses with a guy in her segment. The nudity is sometimes to fast.
Shauna Sand\Playboy Playmate of the Month for May 1996-The nudity is hard to see sometimes
Carrie Stevens\Playboy Playmate of the Month for June 1997-Carrie plays the piano, undresses, becomes topless and eventually nude. Carrie is nude 50% of the time.
Anna Marie Goddard\Playboy Playmate of the Month for January 1994 (40th Anniversary Playmate) & Playmate of the Year for the Dutch edition of Playboy-Very little nudity
Natalia Sokolova\Playboy Playmate of the Month for April 1999-Natalia is fully nude 15% of the time.
Jaime Bergman\Playboy Playmate of the Month for January 1999 (45th Anniversary Playmate)-Due to the poor lighting, it was hard to see Jaime in the nude sometimes.
Laura Cover\Playboy Playmate of the Month for October 1998-Most of the time we see Laura's legs and that is closely follow by her being topless. Laura's nude scenes are not that great.
Stacy Sanches\Playboy Playmate of the Month for March 1995, Playboy Playmate of the Year for 1996 & Germany's Playmate of the Month: Miss June 1996-Stacy is topless or fully nude 100% of the time.
Karen McDougal\Playboy Playmate of the Month for December 1997 & Playboy Playmate of the Year for 1998-Karen slowly strips to full nudity, but most of the time she is shown from the breasts up.
Brooke Richards\Playboy Playmate of the Month for December 1999-Brooke is nude most of the time.
Victoria Silvstedt\Playboy Playmate of the Month for December 1996, Germany's Playmate of the Month for June 1997, & Playboy Playmate of the Year for 1997-Victoria is fully nude 75% of the time.

Also include were thirty Playmates that had five seconds or less spots as well.

The main difference between the VHS and DVD version is the VHS version comes with a preview of Playboy's Best of College Girls and the DVD version come with a slide show of six slides that are not that great. Maybe one day Playboy will get original with its videos. Playboy's Playmates Bustin' Out gets a B-.
